@Comment:	Time is 3:37
@Comment:	Dear Becky I miss you. Ples write back to me. Love Chi (nickname)
@Comment:	context notes say Chi and Mot lie on floor. Chi presses hard but doesn't use other hand as grip. Chi writes independently , asking Mot for help with spelling only. Fat walked into room at the beginning but walked out. Fat came back at the end and laughed with Chi , MOT , and EXP after Chi read the letter. Chi decides who to write to and what to write without prompting from Mot , but Mot has to tell Chi to sign her name. Chi seems confident and at ease with writing
